WEBVTT

00:00.010 --> 00:02.230
In all your years of dealing with the
dead and the dying and the bereaved,

00:02.280 --> 00:04.710
have you ever seen anything
that you could not explain?

00:04.760 --> 00:05.710
Never.

00:05.760 --> 00:08.270
Are you there? Are you with me?

00:08.320 --> 00:10.430
Gabriel drew a picture
of a woman with a book

00:10.480 --> 00:11.950
and so did Harriet.

00:12.000 --> 00:14.550
If you're suggesting that
my pursuit of the truth

00:14.600 --> 00:16.110
is in relation to Gabriel...

00:16.160 --> 00:17.390
Only you can answer that.

00:17.440 --> 00:19.430
God help me, I see the dead

00:19.480 --> 00:22.510
and I have to understand
why this is happening!

00:22.560 --> 00:26.710
You are transgressing
against God and nature.

00:26.760 --> 00:29.590
- Another one of us gone.
- Where does it all end, Gideon?

00:29.640 --> 00:31.070
What do they say about me?

00:31.120 --> 00:32.790
They say you're raising the dead.

00:32.840 --> 00:34.430
Daddy!

00:34.480 --> 00:37.230
Where are you, Daddy?

00:37.280 --> 00:39.400
Nathan? Nathan?

00:40.520 --> 00:42.260
Are you there?

00:42.640 --> 00:44.830
I will protect you.

00:44.880 --> 00:47.420
But can you protect our child?

